nodes.text: Harrison Davis (born February 28, 2003) is the British actor who plays Pommet Warrick in Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker. He is the son of actor Warwick Davis, who plays fellow Ewok Wicket W. Warrick in the film as well as in Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi. He is named after Harrison Ford.
